some common example problem spaces


To make the communication clearer.

Let's say that for this application we have a note taking app, with the
following characteristics: 

- notes are nested
- notes can be pinned (boolean) -> p
- notes can be active , archived or deleted  -> s (status)
- notes can have tags -> t (tags)


When viewing , this ar some examples of the views we can have: 


list active notes
list active pinned notes
list active notes with their children with tags
list active pinned notes with their children with tags created in the last week

and all of the above + search term